import React from "react";

//import reactstrap
import {
  Card,
  CardHeader,
  CardBody,
  Label,
  FormGroup,
  Input,
  Container,
  Row,
  Col,
  Button,
  Form,
} from "reactstrap";

// core components
import SimpleHeader from "components/Headers/SimpleHeader.js";

import { ToastContainer, toast } from "react-toastify";

//React Datepicker
import DatePicker from "react-datepicker";
import "react-datepicker/dist/react-datepicker.css";

function Register() {
  const [startDate, setStartDate] = React.useState(new Date());
  return (
    <>
      <ToastContainer
        position="bottom-right"
        autoClose={5000}
        hideProgressBar={false}
        newestOnTop={false}
        closeOnClick
        rtl={false}
        pauseOnFocusLoss
        draggable
        pauseOnHover
        theme="colored"
      />
      <SimpleHeader name="Register" parentName="Register" />
      <Container className="mt--5">
        <Card>
          <Form>
            <CardBody>
              <Row>
                <Col md="4">
                  <label
                    className="form-control-label"
                    htmlFor="example4cols2Input"
                  >
                    First Name
                  </label>
                  <Input
                    id="example4cols2Input"
                    placeholder="First Name"
                    type="text"
                    // onChange={handleChange("firstname")}
                    // value={staffData.firstname}
                    required
                  />
                </Col>
                <Col md="4">
                  <FormGroup>
                    <label
                      className="form-control-label"
                      htmlFor="example4cols2Input"
                    >
                      Last Name
                    </label>
                    <Input
                      id="example4cols2Input"
                      placeholder="Last Name"
                      type="text"
                      // onChange={handleChange("firstname")}
                      // value={staffData.firstname}
                      required
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Col>
                <Col md="4">
                  <FormGroup>
                    <label
                      className="form-control-label"
                      htmlFor="example4cols2Input"
                    >
                      Enrollment Number
                    </label>
                    <Input
                      id="example4cols2Input"
                      placeholder="Enrollment Number"
                      type="number"
                      // onChange={handleChange("firstname")}
                      // value={staffData.firstname}
                      required
                    />
                  </FormGroup>
                </Col>
              </Row>
              <Row>
                <Col>
                  <label
                    className="form-control-label"
                    htmlFor="exampleFormControlSelect3"
                  >
                    Select Collage
                  </label>
                  <Input
                    id="exampleFormControlSelect3"
                    type="select"
                    // onChange={handleChange("gender")}
                    // value={staffData.gender}
                    required
                  >
                    <option value="" disabled selected>
                      Select Collage
                    </option>
                    <option>SDBCE</option>
                    <option>SDBCT</option>
                  </Input>
                </Col>
                <Col>
                  <label
                    className="form-control-label"
                    htmlFor="exampleFormControlSelect3"
                  >
                    Select Branch
                  </label>
                  <Input
                    id="exampleFormControlSelect3"
                    type="select"
                    // onChange={handleChange("gender")}
                    // value={staffData.gender}
                    required
                  >
                    <option value="" disabled selected>
                      Select Branch
                    </option>
                    <option>A</option>
                    <option>B</option>
                  </Input>
                </Col>
                <Col>
                  <label
                    className="form-control-label"
                    htmlFor="exampleFormControlSelect3"
                  >
                    Select Branch
                  </label>
                  {/* <DatePicker
                    id="exampleFormControlSelect3"
                    className="Period-Time"
                    selected={startDate}
                    onChange={(date) => setStartDate(date)}
                    showTimeSelect
                    showTimeSelectOnly
                    timeIntervals={15}
                    timeCaption="Time"
                    dateFormat="h:mm aa"
                  /> */}
                  <DatePicker
                    id="exampleFormControlSelect3"
                    selected={startDate}
                    onChange={(date) => setStartDate(date)}
                    showYearPicker
                    dateFormat="yyyy"
                  />
                </Col>
              </Row>
            </CardBody>
          </Form>
        </Card>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
}

export default Register;
